General.Name: Rottneros AB
General.Description: Rottneros AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, produces chemical and mechanical market pulp worldwide. The company offers elemental chlorine free bleached long-fiber sulphate pulp used for the manufacture of filters, light cardboard products, and printing and writing papers; and unbleached kraft unbleached long-fiber sulphate pulp used for food packaging and filters, and electrotechnical applications. It also offers bleached/unbleached chemical-thermo-mechanical pulp used for the manufacture of board, printing and writing papers, and tissues. In addition, the company provides moulded fibre trays and customized solutions. Rottneros AB (publ) was founded in 1887 and is based in Söderhamn, Sweden. Rottneros AB (publ) operates as a subsidiary of Arctic Paper S.A.
